WHEREAS, Isaac Herzenberg has brought great pride to his family, his school, his
coaches, and the state of Louisiana through his exceptional achievements, sportsmanship,
and dedication to excellence.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend and congratulate Isaac Herzenberg upon winning his fourth
consecutive Class 2A state track and field championship in the javelin and does hereby
extend best wishes for continued success in his collegiate career and future endeavors.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Isaac
Herzenberg in recognition of his outstanding accomplishments.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
